'''《美國法典》'''（{{lang-en|Code of Laws of the United States of America}}<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20110308201143/http://uscode.house.gov/pdf/2010/2010usc01.pdf Title 1 of the Code] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110308201143/http://uscode.house.gov/pdf/2010/2010usc01.pdf |date=2011-03-08 }} as published by the Office of the Law Revision Counsel</ref>），（Code of Laws of the United States、United States Code、U.S. Code，或縮寫為U.S.C.），是[[美国|美国]]全部联邦法律的官方汇编[[法典|法典]]。共52卷<ref>[https://www.congress.gov/bill/113th-congress/house-bill/1068 Public Law No: 113-287,  To enact title 54, United States Code, "National Park Service and Related Programs", as positive law.]</ref>，另已提出2卷的撰寫計劃<ref>[http://uscode.house.gov/codification/legislation.shtml Office of the Law Revision Counsel]</ref>。[[美國眾議院|眾議院]]{{le|法律修订顾问办公室|Office of the Law Revision Counsel}}每六年出版一次該法典的完全版，但每年亦有增補<ref name="USC">[https://web.archive.org/web/20080216204602/http://www.gpoaccess.gov/uscode/about.html United States Code] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080216204602/http://www.gpoaccess.gov/uscode/about.html |date=2008-02-16 }}</ref><ref name="gpo.gov">[http://www.gpo.gov/help/about_united_states_code.htm About United States Code]. Gpo.gov. Retrieved on 2013-07-19.</ref>。一些未被美國法典收錄的法律見於《[[美国法律总汇|美国法律总汇]]》。

早期对[[美国国会|美国国会]]法律的法典彙編都由私人机构进行。1874年1月22日，美国国会开始进行官方法典彙編活动。1926年，国会正式开始制定《美国法典》。

